                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@Mark, good question! Testing shows that &lt;code&gt;window.decorView&lt;/code&gt; does not work on API 25-29: &lt;code&gt;ViewCompat.getWindowInsetsController()&lt;/code&gt; returns &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt;. &lt;code&gt;currentFocus&lt;/code&gt; has a similar problem on API 30. But you can use any view in your layout, e.g. its root view. For hiding keyboard it works, but for showing keyboard you might be better off with some &lt;code&gt;EditText&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;WindowInsetsControllerCompat.show()&lt;/code&gt; uses it to request focus.&lt;/span&gt;

